public class LineOddsBet
extends OddsBet

Odds bet for the a pass line bet or a come line bet. The payout schedule is as follows:

Point Payout Amount Multiple Example
4, 10 1:2 1 $10 bet pays $20
5, 9 2:3 2 $10 bet pays $15
6, 8 5:6 5 $10 bet pays $12

Author:
Doug Chuchro
